------------------------------------Post----------------------------------------------
1. Add Cart : Method "Post"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/cart/add
3. INPUT: 
   Body -> Raw -> JSON
  
    {
    "userName": "Somi",
    "pass": "somi06",
    "email": "somi6gmail.com",
    "lastName": "samar6",
    "firstName": "sam6",
    "iD": 2
}
-------------------------------------PATCH---------------------------------------------------------------------
1-Add medicine by name to the cart Id and the quantity: Method "Patch"
URL:  http://localhost:9092/cart/2/brofin/2

2- Add medicine by ID to the Cart
   URL:  http://localhost:9092/cart/2/2
   
  
------------------------------------GET----------------------------------------------
1. Get Category By Id : Method "GET"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/cart/getcart/2

1. Get All Category : Method "GET"
2. URL: 	http://localhost:9092/cart/getAll

Get Medicines from the cart:
URL:http://localhost:9092/cart/getMed/2
-----------------------------------------------DELETE-------------------------------------------------------------

1. Delete All Medicines from the cart : Method "DELETE"
 URL:	http://localhost:9092/cart/delete/2
 
2. Delete Medicine from cart by I.D : Delete Method
URL : http://localhost:9092/cart/delete/2/2
	